Standard CPAN module installation:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Requires Perl 5.10 or later.

The test suite includes both unit tests (parsing, async interface, constructors)
and optional integration tests that attempt to connect to a local identd on
port 113. If no identd is running, the integration tests are skipped
automatically — this is normal and expected.
